|---|---|---|
| **P0 (block merge)** | Theme 1 (CI failures), Theme 2.1, Theme 2.2, Theme 3.1, Theme 4.1, Theme 5.1 | Either CI is red, security, or confirmed production bug. |
| **P1 (this PR)** | Theme 2.3, Theme 3.2, Theme 4.2, Theme 6.3, Theme 6.4 | Same blast radius, low cost. |
| **P2 (follow-up PR)** | `@repo/project-urls` consolidation (Theme 5 cross-app), Theme 4.1 Option C (`vendor/db` refactor), Theme 6.1 (GHAS dismiss), Theme 6.2 (defensive try/catch) | Larger scope or low impact. |

### Implementation order within the P0 block

1. `pnpm fix` (clears Theme 1 — biggest noise reduction first).
2. Manual `aria-label` rename in `user-menu.tsx:15`.
3. Three auth race-condition patches (Themes 2.1 + 2.2 + 2.3 — same shape, batch them).
4. `safe-redirect.ts` helper + 3 call-site adoptions + tests (Theme 3.1 + 3.2).
5. `db.runBatch(fn)` rewrite + `org-api-keys.ts` migration + comment fix (Theme 4.1).
6. `apps/platform/src/lib/project-urls.ts` throw-on-missing-VRP + `route.ts:10` comment (Theme 5.1).
7. Drop dead `postgres` dep from `api/app/package.json` (Theme 4.2).
8. `apps/app/next.config.ts` import shared `platformUrl` (Theme 6.3).

